This is jquery plugin for textarea character count, to test this code follow these steps

1. Clone from github

git clone https://github.com/sonchau/textareaCharCount.git

2. cd textareaCharCount

3. open textarea.html on the web browser and start typing

How to use

1. Create a textarea with ID myTextarea and span with ID remainingContainerId

2. Call textarea jquery plugin

<script>
	$('#myTextarea').textareaWordCount({
	  characterLimit: 20,
	  remainingContainerId: "#remainingCharacters"
	});
</script>

NOTE:

- Textarea ID and span ID are required
- characterLimit is optional, if not set it will default to 1000

Jasmine test

Jasmine unit test can be viewed by opening test/runner.html